new?hide_repo_select=true\u0026repo=380863328"},"popovers":{"rename":null,"renamedParentRepo":null},"commitCount":"1","overviewFiles":[{"displayName":"README.md","repoName":"MirzaAbdullah","refName":"main","path":"README.md","preferredFileType":"readme","tabName":"README","richText":"\u003carticle class=\"markdown-body entry-content container-lg\" itemprop=\"text\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch1 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e💫 About Me:\u003c/h1\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content--about-me\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: 💫 About Me:\" href=\"#-about-me\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eWith over 10 years of experience in software development and team leadership, I specialize in building scalable web and mobile applications using technologies like React JS, Redux, RTK Query, React Native, Vue JS, Angular, NgRx, Node JS, and more. I’ve also worked extensively with back-end stacks such as Python, SQLAlchemy, Alembic, C#, .NET Core, and cloud platforms including AWS, GCP, and Azure.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eIn recent years, I’ve focused on AI-powered development, integrating OpenAI, Anthropic, and other LLM APIs into production systems. I’ve built conversational assistants, document summarization tools, and AI-driven dashboards that automate workflows and improve decision-making. My work often involves practical prompt engineering, RAG pipelines, and chat-based UX that bring LLM capabilities directly into user-facing products.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eI also have hands-on experience in Blockchain development, having built analytical bots, automated trading systems, and custom token contracts on the Ethereum network — blending Web3 automation with data-driven logic.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eMy DevOps background includes setting up CI/CD pipelines with GitHub Actions, Jenkins, and Azure DevOps, and configuring observability with Datadog and Sentry to ensure reliability and performance.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eBeyond technical expertise, I lead and mentor cross-functional teams in agile environments, ensuring alignment between business goals and engineering output. I value clear communication, ownership, and iterative improvement as the foundation of high-performing teams.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eI’m passionate about combining AI, automation, and scalable architecture to build products that make complex systems smarter, faster, and more human-friendly.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch2 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e🌐 Socials:\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content--socials\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: 🌐 Socials:\" href=\"#-socials\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 